high_descs: Turn around and go to the teakettle on the left counter.
Pick up the spoon that is on the counter, between the teakettle and toaster.
Turn right and go to the stove.
Put the spoon into the black kettle on the back right stove burner.
Pick up the kettle.
Turn right and go to the right of the sink.
Put the kettle with the spoon in it on the counter, above the right edge of the dishwasher.
anns.task_desc: Place a kettle holding a spoon on a kitchen counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink, turn left to the counter.
Pick up the spoon off of the counter.
Turn right and go to the stove.
Put the spoon in the pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot and spoon from the stove.
Turn right and walk past the sink.
Set the pot and spoon on the counter on the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the pot and spoon on the counter on the right side of the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and start walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the metal spoon that is on the counter to the left of the tea pot.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the oven.
Put the metal spoon in the large black pot that is on the stove top.
Pick up the large metal pot with the spoon in it off of the stove.
Turn right and walk over to the counter, then turn left to face the counter to the right of the sink.
Put the black pot with the spoon in it onto the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a large black pot with a spoon in it on the counter.
